### Contex

The dataset contains information for the number of people taking flights.

### Content

There are two datasets. One training dataset in which there are 18288 rows and 3 columns (ID, Datetime, Count). The test set has 5112 rows and 2 columns (ID, Datetime). A single row represents the number of passengers on a particular date-time. The date in train data is from 25-08-2012 to 25-09-2014. While test data has dated from 26-09-2014 to 15-04-2015.

### Inspiration

With this dataset, you can practice time series, build different models, and learn and try by adding exogenous variables to improve the model accuracy.
